</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="55.[136,1452,312,1051]" pageId="55" pageNumber="146">Etymology. The species name is honoring the Chinese rock singer Mrs. Qi Luo, which encouraged the author by her courage, freedom and spirit of exploration; noun (name) in apposition.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="55.[136,1452,312,1051]" pageId="55" pageNumber="146">
Variation. Male (
<typeStatus box="[370,468,992,1016]" pageId="55" pageNumber="146">paratype</typeStatus>
). Total length 2.05–2.65; prosoma 0.88–0.93 long, 0.73–0.83 wide; sternum 0.50–0.55 long, 0.44–0.50 wide; opisthosoma 0.93–1.13 long, 0.63–0.83 wide.
</paragraph>
